ZH: 自来水是我们日常生活中必不可少的资源之一。
EN: Tap water is one of the essential resources in our daily lives.

ZH: 自来水经过处理后可以直接饮用。
EN: Tap water can be consumed directly after treatment.

ZH: 自来水非常方便，我们只需打开水龙头就可以使用。
EN: Tap water is very convenient, we just need to turn on the tap to use it.

ZH: 自来水的质量有时候会受到污染的影响。
EN: The quality of tap water is sometimes affected by pollution.

ZH: 自来水的价格比瓶装水要便宜很多。
EN: Tap water is much cheaper than bottled water.

ZH: 自来水已经成为城市居民的主要饮用水源。
EN: Tap water has become the main source of drinking water for urban residents.

ZH: 自来水工程已经在世界上许多国家成功实施。
EN: Tap water projects have been successfully implemented in many countries around the world.

ZH: 自来水管道需要定期维护和清洗。
EN: Tap water pipes need regular maintenance and cleaning.

ZH: 自来水对健康有益，含有各类必需的矿物质。
EN: Tap water is beneficial to health as it contains various essential minerals.

ZH: 自来水的消费量每年都在不断增加。
EN: The consumption of tap water increases every year.

ZH: 自来水可以用于洗衣、洗碗和洗澡。
EN: Tap water can be used for laundry, washing dishes, and bathing.

ZH: 自来水的纯净度会受到水质处理设备的影响。
EN: The purity of tap water is influenced by water treatment equipment.

ZH: 自来水来源于市政供水系统。
EN: Tap water comes from the municipal water supply system.

ZH: 自来水工程的实施有助于改善人们的生活条件。
EN: The implementation of tap water projects helps to improve people's living conditions.

ZH: 自来水的供应需要保障其质量和安全性。
EN: The supply of tap water needs to ensure its quality and safety.

ZH: 自来水中的氯含量对人体健康有一定影响。
EN: The chlorine content in tap water has a certain impact on human health.

ZH: 自来水可以直接连接到家庭用具上。
EN: Tap water can be directly connected to household appliances.

ZH: 自来水工程在乡村地区也起到了重要作用。
EN: Tap water projects also play an important role in rural areas.

ZH: 自来水在旅游行业中也起到了重要的作用。
EN: Tap water also plays an important role in the tourism industry.

ZH: 自来水管道系统需要定期检查和维修。
EN: Tap water pipeline systems need regular inspections and maintenance.
